Package: dtlk
Version: 1.0.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: curl, tar
Maintainer: minhyeok <ga111o@proton.me>
Description: DataLink Client - File upload/download tool
 A command-line tool for uploading and downloading files to/from a DataLink server.
 .
 Features:
  - Upload files/directories compressed as tar.gz to server
  - Download and automatically extract files from server  
  - Simple CLI with colored output
  - Automatic duplicate file handling with _dups suffix
  - Comprehensive error checking and user-friendly messages
 .
 The tool compresses specified files/directories into tar.gz archives for upload
 and automatically handles file conflicts during download by renaming duplicates.
Homepage: https://github.com/ga111o/datalink_client
